criteria.inclusion_criteria:
1. Patients with high risk AML, no limit on the gender, aged<60years;
2. KPS score>60, Estimated lifetime>3months;  
3. Patients have HLA matched donor;
4. No serious impairment of important organs; Cr＜1.5mg/dl, Alb≧35g/L, Heart ejection index>55%, Hb>9g/dL, Bilirubin＜2.0mg/dl;
5. No other contraindication of hematopoietic stem cell transplantation;
6. Voluntary participants, informed consent.

criteria.exclusion_criteria:
1. Severe cardiac, renal or hepatic dysfunction;
2. Patients have other malignant cancer and must receive treatment;
3. Patients cant understand or follow study protocol due to clinical symptoms of brain dysfunction or serious mental illness;
4. Patients cant guarantee to accomplish treatment plan and follow-up;
5. Patients with severe  acute hypersensitive reaction;
6. Uncontrolled active infection;
7. Patients who have been enrolled in other clinical trial;
8. Patients arent suitable for this clinical trial according to investigators judgement.
